{"serial": "61014", "department_serial": 55, "code": "AP3111", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Special Topics-Analysis and Application of Meteorology Radar data", "ch": "專題討論-雷達氣象應用"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Liou, Yu-Chieng", "Chung, Kao-Shen", "Chang, Wei-Yu"], "ch": ["廖宇慶", "鍾高陞", "張偉裕"]}, "credits": 1, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "S1", "room": "625"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "大氣科學學系", "en": "Department of Atmospheric Physics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 16, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "此專題主要目的為讓大學部學生認識劇烈天氣觀測與數值模擬，並透過基本實作將理論與實際結合，以瞭解當代中尺度觀測與數值預報之進展。了解雲物理與動力過程，對流系統維持機制等。以專題報告的型式，透過觀測資料分析與數值模擬實驗比對驗證，幫助學生了解實際中尺度天氣個案。此課程內容包含基本文獻導讀，及分組報告建立對中尺度天氣系統的了解。實作部分將介紹相關程式與繪圖，包含雙偏極化雷達資料處理及ＷＲＦ數值模式實驗，建立基本資料處理能力。修課同學將依研究課題，進行雷達觀測，資料同化，數值模擬分組。並需在學期結束前選擇一研究課題，並提交專題研究報告成果。", "en": "The hazard weather events cause great damage to the society all over the world. Most of these events are related to mesoscale meteorology. Different from synoptic- and micro- scale meteorology, the mesoscale weather systems are complex and changeful. The spatiotemporal scan can vary from few kilometers to few thousand kilometers and few minutes to days. With the advanced of the observing technology and numerical model simulation, the understanding of mesoscale weather system has been greatly improved. The main goal of this course is to introduce various mesoscale weather systems including the formation, structure, physical, dynamical and maintaining mechanisms."}, "outline": {"ch": "雷達及中尺度同化、模擬簡介(兩星期)\n中尺度觀測分析文獻回顧 (一星期)\n中尺度模擬、同化分析文獻回顧 (一星期)\n資料處理程式介紹與練習：雙偏極化雷達資料處理與分析(兩星期)\n資料處理程式介紹與練習：中尺度模式資料處理與分析(兩星期)\n專題構想準備(一星期)\n分組研究及準備報告(一～一個半個月)\n成果報告(一星期)", "en": "Introduction of radar, mesoscale meteorology and numerical simulation (two weeks)\nPaper review of mesoscale analysis using observation data (one week)\nPaper review of mesoscale simulation and data assimilation (one week)\nIntroduction of data processing program and practice: dual-polarimetric radar (two weeks)\nIntroduction of data processing program and practice: mesoscale simulation (two weeks)\nResearch project planning (1~1.5 month)\nFinal report"}, "textbook": {"ch": "無", "en": "no"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100", "en": "100"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "研討\n實習/實驗\n個別指導", "en": ["Seminar", "Practical Training Lab", "Individual Instruction"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "論文導讀報告 25％\n實作練習 25％\n期末報告 50％", "en": "paper report 25％\npractice 25％\nfinal report 50％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週一早上", "en": "Monday morning"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "大氣遙測(大氣組)", "en": "大氣遙測(大氣組)"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "數理基礎能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "專業知識能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "資訊應用能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "國際視野與語文溝通能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "專業倫理及服務學習之能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Ability in basic mathematics and science", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in professional knowledge", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in information applications", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in international horizons and communication", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in independent thinking", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": 